# =============================================================================
# travel-planner-root — meta/root repository .gitignore
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The two PRODUCT repos live in their own GitHub repositories and are cloned in
# via init.ps1. They are intentionally ignored here so this root repo only ever
# tracks the shared/meta files (.github AI tooling, .vscode, docs, IATA data).
# =============================================================================

# --- Product repos (own git remotes; reconstruct with init.ps1) ---
/TravelPlanner/
/travel-planner-frontend/

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.user
.vs/

# --- Local secrets / env (never commit) ---
*.env
.env.*
appsettings.*.local.json
